text: Gionges is a former commune. It is in Grand Est in the Marne department in northeast France. On 1 January 2018, it was merged into the new commune of Blancs-Coteaux.Arrêté préfectoral 21 December 2017 == Related pages == * Communes of the Marne department == References == Category:Former communes in Marne
title: Gionges
